{"tid":2064730,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜生日「變裝突襲」謝粉絲！成功偽裝被大讚：台灣 style","createTime":"2020-06-15T04:18:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T05:50:48.000Z","uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a431189295ac337c0f0c7e84d985f65a7338cc03","tid":2064730,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:18:45.000Z","msg":"昨（14）日過 20 歲生日啦！全球粉絲特別串連，在包括韓國地鐵、台北捷運等地買下廣告看板，替子瑜慶生兼宣傳。而子瑜也很有心，在百忙中抽空跑了兩個點拍照留念答謝粉絲的愛，更特別在午夜上傳感性發言，不過眼尖的網友一看子瑜「變裝」的打扮，完全的台灣在地 style，直笑稱果然是我們的台灣女孩！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/06/15/200615-13797-1-sYybJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F06%2F15%2F200615-13797-1-sYybJ.jpg&h=58547650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n子瑜滿20歲生日，突襲粉絲為她慶生看板。"},{"pid":"17c915bca6f24330d1a2a3be8c93f13ec55f4f5b","tid":2064730,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:18:55.000Z","msg":"美麗又不失可愛的子瑜，無論在團體內或個人都擁有高人氣，迎來人生中相當重要的20歲生日之際，更是讓粉絲「預謀」大串連，在各地都買下廣告刊版或影音播放為她慶生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/06/15/200615-13797-2-KSvuv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F06%2F15%2F200615-13797-2-KSvuv.jpg&h=3f7779f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在忙碌的宣傳中，特別抽空跑去粉絲替她慶生的看板拍照。"},{"pid":"636994205411d87f0a114c6694e03267de302eaf","tid":2064730,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:19:09.000Z","msg":"為了答謝粉絲的愛，子瑜也在百忙的宣傳中，特意跑了兩個地方拍照留念，還感性寫道：「很抱歉只去了這兩地方，但我知道還有更多地方在為我慶生還有幫我宣傳生日！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/06/15/200615-13797-3-2qjVr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F06%2F15%2F200615-13797-3-2qjVr.jpg&h=c7cfc40d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「變裝突襲」粉絲為她買下的看板廣告。"},{"pid":"332e907b76a36ac71b89ff68f39a7593f9beb10c","tid":2064730,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:19:13.000Z","msg":"超可愛"},{"pid":"99e84962e1376f7ba5adb6a86c2b8e3ffddaf054","tid":2064730,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:19:24.000Z","msg":"並表示大家的支持對她來說，就已經是個禮物了，「感謝你們再次讓我感受到大家對我的喜愛，每當你們說從我身上得到力量時，其實我也從你們身上得到許多力量，真的很開心也很幸福！Once 謝謝你們！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/06/15/200615-13797-4-nTqpL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F06%2F15%2F200615-13797-4-nTqpL.jpg&h=d25a9aac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為了答謝粉絲的愛，特別跑去留影。"},{"pid":"6e964abfc9deb674e8e3e162a4a02c5ae993bd62","tid":2064730,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:19:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/06/15/200615-13797-7-px3Nx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F06%2F15%2F200615-13797-7-px3Nx.jpg&h=baaf0ddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成員們也紛紛上傳與子瑜的各種合照，祝賀她生日快樂。"},{"pid":"ddd59ffa14104dffe14bb91a564c8763db67ef03","tid":2064730,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:19:46.000Z","msg":"除了感性發言，子瑜也上傳自己「突襲」的照片，只見她特別換上了寬大的T恤與牛仔褲，加上偽裝必備的帽子和口罩，尤其是腳上踩了一雙夾腳涼鞋，更是被網友直呼根本就是「台灣在地 style」！"},{"pid":"3f191bacfca7fcdf4cf9ef723a6c265166f8b969","tid":2064730,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:20:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/06/15/200615-13797-5-lR0K9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F06%2F15%2F200615-13797-5-lR0K9.jpg&h=72778263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/06/15/200615-13797-6-Os7ro.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F06%2F15%2F200615-13797-6-Os7ro.jpg&h=d5ac6916&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這身變裝成功「偽裝」，尤其腳下的一雙夾腳式涼鞋被稱很有台灣味。身打扮被網友直讚偽裝太成功，認為走在路上也完全認不出來！"},{"pid":"12774d53fc864579e1fda4f5068eb051008e372e","tid":2064730,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/06/15/200615-13797-8-ZOtJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F06%2F15%2F200615-13797-8-ZOtJb.jpg&h=d39db419&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網友紛紛狂刷生日留言：「子瑜生日快樂」、「永遠愛妳」！而子瑜的穿搭也被讚：「很接地氣的穿法」、「成功偽裝了」、「跟子瑜同款了」、「感覺涼鞋又要大賣了」！"},{"pid":"1405879009d43e5528b4b407ca1914c272e85174","tid":2064730,"uid":25688,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"又要道歉了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b87c203779509272561c6bdf6a6d280a9b81f8","tid":2064730,"uid":241449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:21:38.000Z","msg":"雞黎渣wor"},{"pid":"0ba8c7148b05d19e12014cc50d1e059caf7c9b19","tid":2064730,"uid":80679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:21:39.000Z","msg":"王怡人屌打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0694db9b6f95ffc59db27974e1f76115da80449","tid":2064730,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:22:38.000Z","msg":"2000年出世已經似27-8是否悲哀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9983fd722181cb3c4a4306d73332742cbd5fac06","tid":2064730,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12774d53fc864579e1fda4f5068eb051008e372e","tid":2064730,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/06/15/200615-13797-8-ZOtJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A